[Information]
AppName: kagetra
Version: 0.0.1
License: MIT Lincense
Developer: Haruhiro Yoshimoto <hpnpwd@gmail.com>
Description: Groupware specialized to Kyogi-Karuta
 
[Middleware]
Version Control System:
  Git
Programming Language:
  Ruby 1.9.3
Ruby Management:
  rbenv + bundler
Web Framework:
  Sinatra + some Padrino modules
Testing:
  RSpec
ORM:
  DataMapper
Database:
  SQLite
HTML Template Engine:
  Haml
CSS Template Engine:
  Sass(SCSS)
Meta JavaScript:
  CoffeeScript
JavaScript Library:
  jQuery
  underscore.js
  Backbone.js
Web UI Library:
  Zurb Foundation 4

[Howto Run]
(0) Prepare Ruby environment
for Ubuntu -> 
  $ apt-get install rbenv
  $ echo 'eval "$(rbenv init -)"' >> ~/.bashrc
  $ rbenv alternatives
  $ cd kagetra && rbenv local 1.9.3-debian
(1) Install bundler
  $ gem install bundler
(2) Install Sinatra and other Ruby modules
  $ cd kagetra && bundle install --path ./.vendor/bundle
(3) Run web app
  $ bundle exec ruby main.rb
